# Root Documentation Sync

- If you create or substantially change root docs, check whether `rules/core/DOCUMENTATION_INDEX.md` must be updated.
- If root/project boundaries change, update `rules/core/PROJECT_MAP.md` and relevant architecture docs.
- Distinguish facts, hypotheses, and decisions in root markdown docs.
- After major work, ensure `RESEARCH_JOURNAL.md` reflects what changed and why.
- Do not leave critical workflow knowledge only in chat if it should persist across sessions.
